Steps to run the test script

1. Install node 6.x.x version (https://nodejs.org/en/blog/release/v6.11.0/)
2. run 'npm install --save-dev' in the source directory, to download all the dependent node modules
3. 'npm run RUN_E2E' to run the Flipkart E2E test suite
4. reports and (error) screenshots can be found in ../reports/

Note: After every successful run, please empty the cart and delete the address given.
This can be handled in the test.before function, to run the suite seamlessly 
